



Dependencies:

To build ls2, you will need to have the following programs, libraries
and their development files:

* gcc (version 4.6 or later)
* python
* GNU Scientific Library (version 1.13 or later)
* HDF5 (version 1.8.4 or later)
* OpenEXR (version 1.6.1 or later)
* cairo (version 1.8.0 or later)
* popt
